      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. so what does that look like in a real workout? like if im trying to maximize that mechanical tension part, should i be doing heavy low reps or is there a specific way the muscle actually reacts to the tension on a cellular level?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
